 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node ELEPH "Elephant Grass"

@{b}Elephant Grass@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = VI(U)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = G
Artist  = Tony Roberts

Text(VI): Cumulative upkeep: <1>
          Black creatures cannot attack you. Nonblack creatures cannot
          attack you unless their controller pays an additional <2> for
          each attacking creature.

Flavor Text: @{i}``How have I angered nature that she would imprison me
               in a labyrinth of grass?'' -Kasib ibn Naji, Letters

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
