@{b}Giant Caterpillar@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = VI(C)
Type    = Summon Caterpillar (3/3)
Cost    = 3G
Artist  = Zina Saunders

Text(VI): <G>, Sacrifice Giant Caterpillar: Put a Butterfly token into
