@{b}King Cheetah@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = VI(C)
Type    = Summon Cheetah (3/2)
Cost    = 3G
Artist  = Terese Nielsen

Text(VI): You may choose to play King Cheetah whenever you could
