@node KYSCU "Kyscu Drake"

@{b}Kyscu Drake@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = VI(U)
Type    = Summon Drake (2/2)
Cost    = 3G
Artist  = G. Darrow & I. Rabarot

Text(VI): <G>: +0/+1 until end of turn. You cannot spend more than <G> in
